commandDescription: list values for a picklist field
sobjecttypeFlagDescription: the sObject type with the picklist field
fieldnameFlagDescription: the name of the picklist field whose values you want to list
resultformatFlagDescription: result format emitted to stdout; --json flag overrides this parameter
errorNoResult: No such field or unable to access field: %s
errorStandardPicklist: Standard picklists are not yet supported: %s
errorGlobalPicklist: Global picklists are not yet supported: %s
errorApiVersion: This plugin requires API >= %s, you are using %s
